<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2036] cassandra-topology.properties cannot reside inside jar file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2036</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PropertyFileSnitch cannot load the cassandra-topology.properties if it is located inside a jar file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At startup cassandra will print and exit&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ERROR&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; 20:50:01  Fatal error: Unable to read cassandra-topology.properties&lt;br/&gt;
Bad configuration; unable to start server&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems FBUtilities.resourceToFIle(..) can only be used for loading plain files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached patch solves the problem. It uses the standard java approach for loading a resource stream...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
